synopsis.text: Dango, Hone Chicken, and a host of delightful, edible characters take center stage in this animated adaptation of San-X's beloved Chickip Dancers mascot series. Led by the energetic and dance-loving frog, Skip Gaeru, this troupe of tasty treats journeys across a stunning world, spreading joy and rhythm wherever they go. At the heart of the story is Hone Chicken, a bone-in chicken with a timid nature and an insatiable curiosity, who finds courage and self-expression through the art of dance. Prepare for a fun-filled adventure that will have you tapping your feet and craving a taste of the action!
